author: @miwable_
text:
I remember watching this mv on MTV, and it keeps repeating because it's their comeback, I guess, but I enjoyed it. I also said to myself back then that if I did get to know each member of this group, I may be a pro at kpop stuff because I am amazed at how many members they have as a group, and I knew like two kpop groups before. And now I know them and each member's name, and I've stan them for like almost three years. I am so grateful to know this amazing group, which gives me happiness I never knew I could find in a K-pop group.

Happy 8th anniversary to one of the groups that is close to my heart, Seventeen. I am always proud of you, my 13 angels. I just wish that I got to know you earlier, but I am still glad that I found you. I will always love and support you on your journey. Let's be together for a long time ‚ô°
